00:05:09.209 --> 00:05:12.319
 He also tried to get sweethearts through MySpace, 

00:05:12.319 --> 00:05:13.782
 but with uneven results. 

00:05:13.782 --> 00:05:15.653
 Sometimes these dates were disappointing, 

00:05:15.653 --> 00:05:19.678
